Freddie Burke Frederick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freddie_Burke_Frederick 0 Freddie Burke Frederick (January 13, 1921 in San Francisco – January 31, 1986 in Glendale, California) was an American child actor. He played Jackie Howell in the 1930 Paramount Pictures film Ladies Love Brutes.
